AMEND S e n ate Bill No. 1612* House Bill No. 2268
by deleting all language after the enacting clause and substituting:
SECTION 1. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 8-50-114(a)(1), is amended by
deleting the following language:
and the waiver shall be used for only one (1) course at a time.
and substituting instead:
and the waiver may be used for more than one (1) course at a time.
SECTION 2. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 8-50-114(h), is amended by deleting
the subsection.
SECTION 3. This act takes effect upon becoming a law, the public welfare requiring it.
